replyTime":"2019-10-18T03:39:51.000Z","msg":"其實你對個運動越上心, 你自自然然就會勇武<br />\n勇武係心態<br />\n<br />\n啲人以為和理非定義只代表唔衝, 就話不如和理非帶下物資啦, <br />\n好可惜我心邊大部份和理非係驚係淆底, 佢地會諗帶啲咁既野被狗逗點算, 於是唔帶。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T05:26:13.000Z","msg":"真！真正既和理非係冇裝修，但絕對會係前線工作支援必要時救人，要有必要時成為勇武既心態"},{"pid":"453e97ec6e2b9e09986f69a6f39ace8e15074402","tid":1661202,"uid":52607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T05:28:43.000Z","msg":"多謝手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c6d32070c1ddc8a4f7b398a204af70d06f1656a","tid":1661202,"uid":9483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T05:29:03.000Z","msg":"蘋果算唔算另類起底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比人篤點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1762da5b4b272267e1ad32bd22d51c773009fb60","tid":1661202,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T05:29:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b4ce4c4a442e802943022ee32234947ccb9fe6","tid":1661202,"uid":198949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T05:32:48.000Z","msg":"言行一致身體力行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src